If you’re feeling a little bloated from all the meat, bread and potatoes you had over the holidays, this zesty chicken satay-style noodle salad will fill you up without leaving you feeling uncomfortable. If you don’t have pineapple, or just don’t like it in your food, you can substitute it with thinned peaches. You can replace the pineapple juice with freshly squeezed orange juice. Ingredients ALSO SEE: Recipe of the day: Chutney mayo pork chops with creamy mash *This recipe was found on www.jamieoliver.com.